Author: Oracle Version: 11.1 Last update: May-2008
Description: - Integration Knowledge Module - Integrates data in a Netezza target table in truncate / insert (append) mode. - Data can be controlled. Invalid data is isolated in the Error Table and can be recycled.
Restrictions: - When using the RECYCLE_ERRORS option, you have to set an Update Key for your interface. - When using this module with a journalized source table, data is automatically filtered to not include source deletions. - The FLOW_CONTROL and STATIC_CONTROL options call the Check Knowledge Module to isolate invalid data (if no CKM is set, an error occurs). Both options must be set to NO in the case when an Integration Interface populates a TEMPORARY target datastore.
Change History: May-2008 - Update of description - Updated to odiRef - 5995092 fixed
Automatically attempts to insert data into the Target Datastore of the Interface
Commit all data inserted in the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to perform flow control.
Check this option to recycle data rejected from a previous control.
Check this option to control the target table after having inserted or updated target data.
Check this option if you wish to truncate the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to delete all the rows of the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to create the target table
The integration table distribution key is based on the target table primary key.
The integration table distribution is performed on a round-robin distribution.

<%if ( odiRef.getUserExit("FLOW_CONTROL").equals("1") ) { %> insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","A")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> <%=odiRef.getColList(",", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and TRG) and REW)")%> ) select <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> <%=odiRef.getColList(",", "[EXPRESSION]", ",
	", "", "((INS and TRG) and REW)")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","INT_NAME","A")%> <% } else { %> insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","A")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "(INS and REW)")%> ) select <%=odiRef.getPop("DISTINCT_ROWS")%> <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[EXPRESSION]", ",
	", "", "(INS and REW)")%> from <%=odiRef.getFrom()%> where <% if (odiRef.getPop("HAS_JRN").equals("0")) { %> (1=1) <%} else {%> JRN_FLAG <> 'D' <% } %> <%=odiRef.getJoin()%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getGrpBy()%> <%=odiRef.getHaving()%> <% } %>

<%if ( odiRef.getUserExit("FLOW_CONTROL").equals("1") ) { %> insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","INT_NAME","W")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "INS and REW")%> ) select <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "INS and REW")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","INT_NAME","W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> T where <%=odiRef.getColList("", "T.[COL_NAME]	= E.[COL_NAME]", "
		and	", "", "UK")%> ) and E.ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and E.ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' <% } %>

<%if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_METHOD"))){%> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> update <%=odiRef.getTable( "L" , "JRN_NAME" , "A" )%> set JRN_CONSUMED = '1' where (1=1) <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","INT_NAME","A")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> ) select <%=odiRef.getPop("DISTINCT_ROWS")%> <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[EXPRESSION]", ",\n\t", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> from <%=odiRef.getFrom()%> where <% if (odiRef.getPop("HAS_JRN").equals("0")) { %> (1=1) <%} else {%> JRN_FLAG <> 'D' <% } %> <%=odiRef.getJoin()%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getGrpBy()%> <%=odiRef.getHaving()%>

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","JRN_NAME","A")%> where JRN_CONSUMED = '1' <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

create table <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "INT_NAME", "A")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]\t[DEST_WRI_DT] " + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL"), ",\n\t", "", "INS")%> ) <% if ("1".equals(odiRef.getOption("DISTRIBUTE_PK_INT"))) { %> DISTRIBUTE ON (<%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ", ", "", "PK")%>) <%} else if ("1".equals(odiRef.getOption("DISTRIBUTE_RND_INT"))) { %> DISTRIBUTE ON RANDOM <%} %>
